column5: ....I guess not many hunters would want to bag this kind of a trophy....  7-legged deer killed in FdL County

They should have taken a pic of the deer.  Would be interesting to see things like this in stead of just a report. Just mu opinion as proof.   But then again maybe better not see it Or I'll get sick to my stomach. LOL   dsn
Not a bad deal. 1 deer, 7 lamps.
dsn, there was a link to more pictures of that deer at the bottom of the article. Not what we pictured in our minds though. Small appendages at best, not full grown legs.
wouldnt really wanna eat that guy... lol
His daddy musta been a spider
now if we could get turkeys with 7 legs, I would be a happy camper
